Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.78,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one girl left to beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna go rough on a little girl\Nbut I've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to put the Tatababasco grape\Ninto Sugar's mouth somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trebol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you got \Nbeaten by a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou idiot. Drop dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead yet, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! If you'd just kept running,\Nyou might have survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you took the trouble\Nto come back to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:57.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ROYAL PALACE 2ND FLOOR - THE SUIT CHAMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report that you, \Nsir, were on the 1st floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean somebody who\Nlooked like him was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen anybody\Nwho looks like me in the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}King Riku-sama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This sword looks good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can turn back into a human,\NI wanna use this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was fighting \Nin the Colosseum today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe Doflamingo's abdication\Nwas a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just this morning\Nand we all lost patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}King Riku-sama was fighting \Nin the Colosseum?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A boy committed a murder!\NTwo people got killed in a squabble in the slum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The boy is now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:07.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A BOY IN THE SLUM - KYROS (15 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he move like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way! He's just a boy!\N--But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}! What are you doing?!\NIt's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's just a boy,\Nhe's an infamous thug!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're the king or not!\NWhoever approaches me will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king is in danger! Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't shoot!\NPut your guns down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you fought dozens of hooligans\Non your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And more than the half of them got injured
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and two of them got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ganged up on my best friend\Nand killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was just getting revenge for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a beast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say whatever you like!\NA royal person like you can't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only person I trusted\Nin the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was like a brother to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Kyros, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from him, King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 15-year-old murderer - Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe's gonna fight against an experienced gladiator!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Colosseum is a sacred place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A murderer like you doesn't belong here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna keep looking \Nat the sword, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sword's blade may be blunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut prepare to get some of your limbs broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it! Kyros wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner is the 15-year-old \Nmurderer - Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's not over yet!\N--That's enough! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so talented!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the blade wasn't blunt, he \Nwould've killed his opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbarism looks a lot \Nlike a talent here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Kyros doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He nearly killed all the convict \Ngladiators in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't eaten for six days\Nand just keeps shouting "Call King Riku."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kyros?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku! What are you gonna do with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna execute me, do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me or hang me or whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die so badly?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you regretting what you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret? I thought you were different\Nand you understood me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! Just kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gladiatorial contest that \Nyou fought in the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't just a deadly competition or a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been going on for several centuries\Nin this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sacred event in which \Nfighters discipline their mind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand hone their sword skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to become a gladiator?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gladiator? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0} is planning \Nto release you on parole
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once you win 100 matches in \Nas much time as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,FOUR MONTHS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick the murderer's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring down Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros wins 20 consecutive matches!\NHe's unbelievably strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyros wins 50 consecutive matches!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros wins 100 out of 100 matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NEven the star gladiator couldn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally won his freedom\Nin such a short period of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could anyone be that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come out, murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone like him gets released,\Nhe may kill more people again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She's right.\N--Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Don't come back \Non the street, murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:11:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't release him!\N--Keep fighting until you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go out where people don't want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you want to become \Nthe person other people wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People like beasts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as long as they stay...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in a cage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I get out of the cage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there is no place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...for me to go back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nowhere for me to belong out there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His 200th win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:12:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Somebody, bring down Kyros!\N--Defeat Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His 300th win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop Kyros!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes have been brought \Ndown one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally - an unprecedented 1000th victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:19.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HIS 4TH YEAR AT THE COLOSSEUM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ire of the crowd\Nturned to adulation before I knew it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kyros.\N--Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where I go,\NI'll be a beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who killed men for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everybody would forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious tough man who \Ncame into sudden prominence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ngoing by "Ricky", is fighting Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The odds are for Kyros who will mark \Nhis 3000th win if he wins this match
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ricky isn't giving up an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Ricky landed a blow against Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros has never taken a single hit\Nfrom an opponent before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:15:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won 3000 out of 3000 in nine years!\NHe's never lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The living legend - Kyros!\NThe word "invincible" truly only fits to this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you enter secretly,\NKing Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became quite strong after you \Ntaught me how to fight, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you lowered your guard \Nwhen you noticed it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou're not such a "beast" after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that enough now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've spent your life locked away \Nin this "cage" for nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to leave now.\NThere's something I need you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than regretting \Nwhat you did in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyou can save many lives from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one way for you to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:16:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros! We'll be counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A YEAR LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros! Thank you always for your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:12.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE COMMANDER OF THE DRESSROSA KING RIKU ARMY\NKYROS (25 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Kyros-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls love you so much, huh?!\NKyros-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Nlets you in to the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Princess-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis, don't!\NYou can't bring up his old pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he even assigned you\Nto be the commander of the righteous army!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can fool the whole \Nnation, you can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:45.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE PRINCESS OF DRESSROSA \N- SCARLET (15 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll reveal your true colors someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me and my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:54.37,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But Big Sis, he's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:57.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE SECOND PRINCESS (THE YOUNGER SISTER) -\NVIOLA (10 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't look into his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mind is corrupted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm responsible for protecting you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.26,0:17:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lady Scarlet has been kidnapped!\N--They were pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What happened to her bodyguards?!\N--They all got beaten up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just calm down!\N--Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's gonna come rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we get a lot of \Nmoney from King Riku as ransom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand just sell her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea! She's a real princess!\NWe can make a good price!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay close behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:18:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Lady Scarlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I touched you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros! I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis is cooking something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna resign as my daughters' bodyguard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWhy're you saying that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're in love with Scarlet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NN-No, I'm not! I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest hero in the \Nhistory of the Colosseum
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the commander of the \Narmy. And the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know each individual will \Ncelebrate your marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but social constraints\Nwon't allow your criminal record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how public life works.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\NIf I can't marry him, I'd rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a sudden illness.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she would've become \Na great queen someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlet. As of today,\Nyou're not a member of the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People think you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I'm repaying your kindness \Nwith ingratitude, King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were anyone else but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros! I've never heard a story like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.89,0:21:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros, hold her in your arms.\NShe's your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't touch such an innocent thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are tainted!\NI don't wanna taint her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is a strange man, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.31,0:21:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like an angel, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching over you!\NI'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peek-a-boo! Your grandpa is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca! You got big again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}, take off your disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gloves, gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute she is! How cute she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd never expected that\NI could have such happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it didn't last long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.66,0:22:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was 10 years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}10 years ago, the Toy Soldier was tragically torn\Nfrom his loved ones!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shouldering the burden of \Neverybody's expectations,
